        "id": "DocumentReference.identifier:entryUUID",
        "path": "DocumentReference.identifier",
        "sliceName": "entryUUID",
        "short": "Business identifier for the DocumentReference",
        "definition": "The Business identifier for the DocumentReference which maps to the DocumentEntry.entryUUID in XDS. This is used to refer to the DocumentReference itself as a record of the Document's metadata, as opposed to the UniqueId element which identifies the document which is pointed at by the document reference. This element SHALL NOT be provided by the client for simplified publish and will instead be assigned by the server.",
